{"tid":157611,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人細過養過巴西龜","createTime":"2017-03-15T15:38:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-18T08:47:30.000Z","uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f1e64ddbf2189170706b9be1019f50408ff54ac4","tid":157611,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T15:38:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最長幾耐命？<br />\n(細個我養個啲半年就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"},{"pid":"0088e02179704ad7af83fec9174dde1d3a25dcc9","tid":157611,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T15:39:30.000Z","msg":"我養兩隻<br />\n三個月就死咗"},{"pid":"5fb65f69406feb4366c73903947cefce76fad3c6","tid":157611,"uid":14240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T15:40:33.000Z","msg":"中一養到而家yr2"},{"pid":"e223fe70e6b394680b8c3841c7a8305e02b4b1df","tid":157611,"uid":89337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T15:42:01.000Z","msg":"養左10幾年 但係最近半年左右先開始裝過濾器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n未裝之前係每幾日就換一次水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有養左隻草龜陪佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a49884da7d8bf32f029e63ed4eca2a89cfa70f65","tid":157611,"uid":8911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T15:43:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最長幾耐命？<br />\n(細個我養個啲半年就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)</blockquote><br />\n我仲有淨一隻，好耐，應該有四十歲"},{"pid":"961981e86f1d6f0022a4578b65df15b985151056","tid":157611,"uid":70085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T15:44:50.000Z","msg":"養過幾隻，次次唔夠一個月就盲，跟住無幾耐就死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a48f7470413e1726ba1c413120be9334a77b50b5","tid":157611,"uid":89337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T15:46:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>養過幾隻，次次唔夠一個月就盲，跟住無幾耐就死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解會盲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b15e27f72cbb91cc0c74a507e783d41aa01214c","tid":157611,"uid":35878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T15:48:06.000Z","msg":"小學養過，科學堂教啲龜要冬眠，咁冬天就到時將隻龜用毛巾包好，擺入鞋盒，放係床下底俾佢冬眠。<br />\n到春天拎返佢出黎，已經變左龜乾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，好似海味鋪有碌竹插住個啲四腳蛇乾咁。<br />\n我都唔知點解會咁，有次中文堂寫週記功課寫左呢單野，老師評語解釋返香港屬於亞熱帶，龜唔駛冬眠，我先知發生咩事。<br />\n跟住搵個食物盒，裝啲水，冚好蓋，再包十幾層保鮮紙，係屋企樓下既花槽埋左佢等佢好好安葬。<br />\n再後來先知原來膠係十幾年都唔會化，所以照計而家佢應該仲係個食物盒裡面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fcf7ab5b9c06e2d415bf6dc133035edb67a8c2b","tid":157611,"uid":78769,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T15:48:09.000Z","msg":"幾個月便死了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65ace00130cfd37fb7399877c87169be736253ff","tid":157611,"uid":70085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T15:49:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>養過幾隻，次次唔夠一個月就盲，跟住無幾耐就死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解會盲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都唔知，但係次次養養吓就會有一隻眼唔開"},{"pid":"ef122e736f71c9780691e4e30e29756a31f75131","tid":157611,"uid":24976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T15:54:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r4Y8qU4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr4Y8qU4.jpg&h=8acd3955&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n養左差唔多1年，一隻好驚人，一隻成日伸個頭俾我摸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"677cb1f86247340f3c2ce71c2dda3a8142053dd1","tid":157611,"uid":9457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T15:56:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>養過幾隻，次次唔夠一個月就盲，跟住無幾耐就死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解會盲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都唔知，但係次次養養吓就會有一隻眼唔開</blockquote><br />\n水有氯氣 無隔夜會整盲佢"},{"pid":"c149841cb9d589f221a82e0c0c5af08448721480","tid":157611,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T21:01:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>養過幾隻，次次唔夠一個月就盲，跟住無幾耐就死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解會盲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都唔知，但係次次養養吓就會有一隻眼唔開</blockquote><br />\n水有氯氣 無隔夜會整盲佢</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好慘，龜仔睇唔到野"},{"pid":"a01e02c998ce4ee9a0877eb6741126f29cfeda19","tid":157611,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T21:02:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r4Y8qU4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr4Y8qU4.jpg&h=8acd3955&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n養左差唔多1年，一隻好驚人，一隻成日伸個頭俾我摸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />想摸龜頭，以前個隻咬我手指<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d027854fa00912aa9f006df8367e38bb8be16391","tid":157611,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T21:03:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小學養過，科學堂教啲龜要冬眠，咁冬天就到時將隻龜用毛巾包好，擺入鞋盒，放係床下底俾佢冬眠。<br />\n到春天拎返佢出黎，已經變左龜乾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，好似海味鋪有碌竹插住個啲四腳蛇乾咁。<br />\n我都唔知點解會咁，有次中文堂寫週記功課寫左呢單野，老師評語解釋返香港屬於亞熱帶，龜唔駛冬眠，我先知發生咩事。<br />\n跟住搵個食物盒，裝啲水，冚好蓋，再包十幾層保鮮紙，係屋企樓下既花槽埋左佢等佢好好安葬。<br />\n再後來先知原來膠係十幾年都唔會化，所以照計而家佢應該仲係個食物盒裡面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />過多千年就冇事架啦<br />\nbtw 龜乾真係好癲"},{"pid":"7a75e2b7d2e24bebd40ca5d881b28f40cb7caf36","tid":157611,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T21:03:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>養左10幾年 但係最近半年左右先開始裝過濾器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n未裝之前係每幾日就換一次水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有養左隻草龜陪佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />單身咗十幾年"},{"pid":"99dab982294871a4b18f3bf6f85d5ddc8a885736","tid":157611,"uid":80944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T23:51:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63fa0542fb3370bb1c319f43a4f04c6c004e492b","tid":157611,"uid":90980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T09:41:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r4Y8qU4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr4Y8qU4.jpg&h=8acd3955&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n養左差唔多1年，一隻好驚人，一隻成日伸個頭俾我摸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n左邊係豹龜？好得意"},{"pid":"e3ab1